function Start()

	local idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	local id_Clone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_RAKHAAN)
	
	local tPath = Hydra.PathsLinkedByActor(ID_RAKHAAN, "Path")
	Hydra.QActorFollowPathDynamicSpeed(id_Clone, tPath[1], "NPC_Run", false)
	Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(id_Clone)

	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_RAKHAAN_ARRIVE, idOwner, id_Clone)

end
